sentences: Inger Wikstrom (born 11 December 1939) is a Swedish pianist, composer and conductor.
She married David Bartov and the couple moved with their three children to Österskär, where they opened the Nordic Music Conservatory in 1977, which became the Nordic Chamber Opera in 1980.
